# Tech Stack

**Primary language**: Python

## Languages & Versions

- **Python**: 100.0% of codebase

## Runtime Versions

- python: >=3.11,<4.0

> Always match these versions. Do not introduce APIs from newer runtime versions.

## Frameworks

- **fastapi** (web)

> Use only the frameworks listed above. Never introduce a new framework or major dependency without explicit approval.


## Package Managers

pip

> Use **pip** for all dependency operations. Do not mix package managers.
